Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.43,0:00:45.44,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I look up to the sky after the rain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.43,0:00:45.44,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ame agari no sora wo aogu tabi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:51.15,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I think back to when I was a crybaby
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:51.15,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nakimushi datta koro no boku wo omou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:58.91,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I was chasing somebody's back blindly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:58.91,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,dareka no senaka wo gamushara ni oikaketa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.03,0:01:01.79,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking "I want to be stronger"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.03,0:01:01.79,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"tsuyoku naritai" tte
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.95,0:01:07.29,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The word "thank you" has faded into the wind now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.95,0:01:07.29,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ima wa kaze ni kieta "arigatou"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.37,0:01:12.38,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I getting stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.37,0:01:12.38,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,boku wa tsuyoku nareteiru no kana?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.51,0:01:18.05,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the answer yet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.51,0:01:18.05,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kotae wa mada desou ni nai kara sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.09,0:01:23.39,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yappari mada aruiteiku yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.09,0:01:23.39,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'll keep walking ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.64,0:01:25.81,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,saa yukou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.64,0:01:25.81,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:29.11,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tachidomaru koto naku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:29.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Without stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.23,0:01:34.44,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nagareru toki ni makenai youni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.23,0:01:34.44,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Without giving up to the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:39.91,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nando mo tachimukai tsuzukeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:39.91,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep getting back up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.03,0:01:45.41,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,taisetsu na mono ushinaitakunai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.03,0:01:45.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to lose something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:50.84,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,boku no naka ni nagareru koe wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:50.84,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The voice inside of me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:56.01,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,zutto zutto boku wo sasaeteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:56.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,keeps sustaining me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:02:01.26,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,itazura na ame ga jama suru kedo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:02:01.26,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wicked rain will get in my way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:06.10,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nigedasanai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:06.10,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't walk away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:11.69,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,saa yukou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:11.69,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:14.98,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Tachidomaru koto naku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:14.98,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Without stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:20.16,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nagareru toki ni makenai youni
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:20.16,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Without giving up to the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.28,0:02:25.83,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nando mo tachimukai tsuzukeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.28,0:02:25.83,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep getting back up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:31.46,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,taisetsu na mono ushinaitakunai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:31.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to lose something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.59,0:02:39.68,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shinjita sono saki e to...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.59,0:02:39.68,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To the future I believe in...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.88,0:02:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is the \NGreat Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.70,0:02:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Countless pirates fight \Ndesperately for the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.02,0:02:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the great treasure left behind by \NGold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.65,0:03:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned \Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.55,0:03:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,also takes to the sea to become \Nthe next King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.34,0:03:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Luffy and his friends \Novercome numerous adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.39,0:03:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the World Government is less and \Nless able to ignore their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.33,0:03:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.84,0:03:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of adventure \Nis waiting for us next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.76,0:03:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crew, on its way \Nto the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.22,0:03:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will speed along the \NGrand Line again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.15,0:03:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Separated from the rest of the Straw Hats,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.55,0:03:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy is headed to the Navy Headquarters in order to rescue his brother, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.78,0:03:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, there are only 3 hours left before the public execution of Portgaz D. Ace...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.78,0:04:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ticking Down to the Time of Battle! The Navy's Strongest Lineup in Position!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.06,0:04:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.86,0:05:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Climb.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.17,0:06:05.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,1)}"South Blue"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.12,0:06:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's in 3 hours now! I wonder if Whitebeard has arrived yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. Do you think he's really gonna be there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.30,0:06:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a big deal but isn't he too old?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.57,0:06:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.39,0:06:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was around before the Great Pirate Era. He must be senile by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.01,0:06:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't heard his name in any big news for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.56,0:06:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you guys take this so lightly?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.91,0:06:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he's unignorable, the Navy HQ has called up its elites and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is expecting him with all their forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.14,0:06:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm almost certain that Whitebeard is going to appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.20,0:06:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then what's gonna happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.22,0:06:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. How am I supposed to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:55.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,1)}"East Blue"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.58,0:06:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a pirate of a different era.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.46,0:07:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it possible for him to beat the Navy HQ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.31,0:07:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not possible for any pirates to attack Marineford.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.36,0:07:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true. I think it was 20 years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.89,0:07:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a pirate called Shiki the Golden Lion invaded Marineford
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.74,0:07:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and left the Navy HQ half destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.33,0:07:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time it's going to be worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.23,0:07:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter who wins, a lot of people will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.32,0:07:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be better if he didn't appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.44,0:07:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If nothing besides the execution happens, that'd be for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.10,0:07:43.31,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,1)}"North Blue"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.28,0:07:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, we want drinks, old guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.61,0:07:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you asking me to open the bar on a day like this? We're expecting a big war in any minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.67,0:07:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home! If the world's still here tomorrow, I'll open it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then just sell us some drinks! It feels like we're the ones who're on the scaffold!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.87,0:08:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't do without drinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.91,0:08:11.51,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not just another old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.21,0:08:13.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,1)}"West Blue"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.51,0:08:13.97,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't lost it at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.97,0:08:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just a year ago, when we saw him sitting right there...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.69,0:08:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we thought we were dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.27,0:08:33.24,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,1)}"Grand Line"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.93,0:08:33.24,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Whitebeard that outrageous?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.19,0:08:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even those kids know it. They're singing as they jump rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pirate Whitebeard is scarier than a devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.51,0:08:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.34,0:08:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is this world headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the island of Marineford home of the Navy Headquarters,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.50,0:09:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lies a huge city mainly populated by families of the Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.29,0:09:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An evacuation order has been issued to all residents at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.80,0:09:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And at Sabaody Archipelago at the evacuation site,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.45,0:09:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,residents are watching the proceedings of the execution on monitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.10,0:09:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reporters and cameramen from various places are...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.20,0:09:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...standing by here to break the news quickly to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.37,0:09:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's really the best of Navy HQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.20,0:09:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I assume that Whitebeard knows about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.29,0:10:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But still, will he venture to be there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.37,0:10:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every look-out ship that the Navy sent has been swiftly sunk
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.34,0:10:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and there has been no report of a sighting of Whitebeard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.41,0:10:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the tension at Marineford continues to rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.72,0:10:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there is less than 3 hours left until the looming execution.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.77,0:10:28.64,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Navy"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.80,0:10:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have problem with that. Is that really necessary?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.87,0:10:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This public execution is not just an execution of a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.37,0:10:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has great significance for the future of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.51,0:11:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why it's necessary to...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.53,0:11:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are responsible for this matter since you are one of the parties involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.01,0:11:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget that, Garp.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.71,0:11:34.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Marineford Navy Headquarters"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.69,0:11:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you, don't lag behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.66,0:12:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't slacken your pace!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.04,0:12:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens, it'll last only 3 hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's all finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.24,0:12:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elite soldiers are summoned from all over the world--totaling almost one hundred thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.76,0:12:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crescent-shaped bay area and the whole island are surrounded by 50 Navy ships
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.63,0:12:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and numerous cannons have been set at the bay area.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.72,0:12:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And in front of all the marshaled forces that can be seen from sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.61,0:12:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...stand 5 ruffians who hold the key to the war. Pirates--The Seven Warlords!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.50,0:12:54.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}"Bartholomew Kuma"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.54,0:12:58.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}"Gecko Moria"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.46,0:13:02.34,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}"Don Quixote Doflamingo"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.38,0:13:06.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}"Dracule Mihawk"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.34,0:13:10.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}"Boa Hancock"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.41,0:13:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.72,0:13:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the admirals!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.29,0:13:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why but I find them so intimidating!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.13,0:13:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guarding closely below the scaffold are...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.88,0:13:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Navy's greatest powers...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.98,0:13:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the three admirals!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:39.92,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(540,1)}"Navy Admiral\NAokiji Kuzan"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.38,0:13:44.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(540,1)}"Navy Admiral\NAkainu Sakazuki"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:48.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(540,1)}"Navy Admiral\NKizaru Borsalino"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.49,0:13:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every force of justice imaginable is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.03,0:14:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...now waiting for the Whitebeard Pirates to stop them from rescuing Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.01,0:14:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.12,0:14:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to live without leaving any regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.09,0:14:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.32,0:15:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta go out to sea someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.18,0:15:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and live as we like.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.07,0:15:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Freer than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.15,0:15:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.61,0:15:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Jimbei!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.43,0:16:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see the Gate of Justice already! That was fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.02,0:16:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it wasn't! If the wind were right, we could have gotten here faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.03,0:16:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.14,0:16:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I warn you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.27,0:16:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we don't open the Gate of Justice, you guys can't get to Marineford
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.59,0:16:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or even get out of the Tub Current!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.71,0:16:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no sea for you all to get away to or to live on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.28,0:16:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So now, how can we get through the gate?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.17,0:16:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys! It's almost time for...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.47,0:16:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.06,0:16:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time for Captain Buggy to conquer the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.32,0:16:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy HQ is nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whitebeard is nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.33,0:16:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is the next King of the Pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.49,0:16:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.71,0:17:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.41,0:17:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buggy! Buggy! Buggy! Buggy! Buggy! Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.46,0:17:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.53,0:17:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look! "Fire Fist" Ace has come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.70,0:17:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the man...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.06,0:17:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...who may trigger a war that will shake the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.26,0:18:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he is the one who holds the fate of the world now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.15,0:18:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Garp? I'll tell them everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.99,0:18:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So be it. I'll be downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.40,0:18:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Step aside for a minute.\N--Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.81,0:18:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Fleet Admiral Sengoku!\N--What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.05,0:19:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Give me a Transponder Snail.\N--Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.21,0:19:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something to tell you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.36,0:19:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Portgaz D. Ace...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.38,0:19:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about the great significance of his death today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.76,0:19:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.43,0:19:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Women are very sweet at times like this, Tsuru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace, tell them the name of your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.79,0:19:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father? Why is that important now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.96,0:20:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father is Whitebeard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.63,0:20:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.67,0:20:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he is! Whitebeard is my only father!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.78,0:20:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We looked for you with our eyes wide open at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.58,0:20:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because we heard that there might be a child of that man on some island.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.81,0:20:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Based on a small amount of reliable information from Cipher Pol,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.32,0:20:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we checked all newborns...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.41,0:20:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and preborn children...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.36,0:20:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and their mothers but we couldn't find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.14,0:20:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.01,0:20:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mother risked her life to bear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.14,0:20:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She used a trick that can be called mother's pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.39,0:20:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That has misled us... Indeed, the whole world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.02,0:20:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is an island called Batelira in the South Blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.98,0:21:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mother's name is Portgaz D. Rouge.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.46,0:21:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She did something that completely defied natural law...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.74,0:21:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...for the love of her child.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.79,0:21:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She kept her baby inside her womb for 20 months!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.57,0:21:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.51,0:21:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And as soon as she gave birth to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.02,0:21:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she lost all of her strength and passed away right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.81,0:21:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A year and 3 months after the father's death,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.19,0:21:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the child was born with the blood of the world's most heinous man in his veins.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.74,0:21:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.46,0:21:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know it, surely?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.06,0:22:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can't blame a child whose not born.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.96,0:22:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garp!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.56,0:22:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look after my child!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.11,0:22:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.68,0:22:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the King of the Pirates -
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.15,0:22:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.35,0:22:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Fire Fist" Ace is a son of Gold Roger?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.25,0:22:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is huge news.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.62,0:22:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call the head office! Let's issue an extra!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.69,0:22:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it continue?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.53,0:23:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.00,0:23:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bloodline of the King of the Pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.29,0:23:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The secret of Ace's origin has been revealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.25,0:23:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His father Roger's feelings, and his mother\NRouge's strong resolve lay behind it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.35,0:23:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At Marineford, Whitebeard's fleet silently approaches.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.64,0:23:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.07,0:23:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Vast Fleet Appears! Here Come the Whitebeard Pirates!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.95,0:23:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
